{"comments":"Aspect ratio container component\n\nMaintains consistent aspect ratios for responsive content like\nimages, videos, embeds, and other media.\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Layout.AspectRatio as AspectRatio\n\n-- 16:9 video container\nAspectRatio.aspectRatio [ AspectRatio.ratio AspectRatio.R16x9 ]\n  [ HH.video [ HP.src \"video.mp4\" ] [] ]\n\n-- Square image container\nAspectRatio.aspectRatio [ AspectRatio.ratio AspectRatio.R1x1 ]\n  [ HH.img [ HP.src \"avatar.png\" ] ]\n\n-- Custom aspect ratio\nAspectRatio.aspectRatio [ AspectRatio.customRatio 21 9 ]\n  [ content ]\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Aspect ratio container\n\nChildren are positioned to fill the container while maintaining\nthe specified aspect ratio. The container is responsive and will\nscale based on its parent width.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"w","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"i","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Layout","AspectRatio"],"AspectRatioProp"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Halogen","HTML","Core"],"HTML"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"w","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"i","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"tag":"ParensInType"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],